Let the preservatives not only be behind the pults, but those hundred let them be in the dosers on public toilets, in places where young people often go.
“It’s not promiskuity.
It’s not about paying them a beer and a motel, as Governor Emilio González responded to the question whether he would agree to the distribution of preservatives in his district.
“The best thing is to make preservatives available to those who already have a sexual life,” he said.
Key numbers in Jalisco
There were 13 435 cases (12 158 cases of AIDS and 1 317 cases of HIV).
This state means in Mexico the fourth place in new and detected cases of AIDS and the 13th place in connection with HIV.
92% of the infection occurs by sex, 6% by blood and 2% perinatal.
